er  Section: 544 - A Cr.P.C.   recoverable as arrears of land  revenue and in default of payment of compensation  amount to further undergo S.I. for six months.  Under Section :  3 24   PPC  “ Seven   Y ears’ Rigorous Imprisonment ”   (for an attempt to  commit   Qatal - e - Amd   of Babar Tariq /injured )   with fine of  Rs.1 0,000/ -   and in default thereof to further undergo S.I. for  six   months.
