Pakistan ko apne akhrajat ko pura karne keliye foreign countries se madad lena parti hai/parta tha.



NOTE 1:

For past tense, nashani for such sentences is that ‘parta tha’ jaise alfaz  Urdu sentences ke akhar ma attain hain, therefore, had to ks istemal kiya jata hai.  

                   

